 "768312218730772", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031436_768312222064105_2483983745682146754_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=8R0r54OkobsQ7kNvgF237GP&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAMX0TdLvuXYCL2hMEimGHwrpGJsbu-ufjVPYkfheklSA&oe=66D1C79E"}, {"file_name": "com.ypro.project_y-20240210-1504414_2.png", "id": "1144388200046417", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39003227_1144388210046416_8982093088097178928_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=qnu6iL85QS0Q7kNvgFps9jq&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCOPkbRpA5y_xTiFtv310H7e7y4EJTlK3XSHtEzKO6FLg&oe=66D1A091"}, {"file_name": "com.ypro.project_y-20240210-115437.png", "id": "1405118490144295", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75230048_1405118493477628_4689660376237645316_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=KueYRhQGvuoQ7kNvgE1s4Ji&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBNGIst7OpdxwD4RG_d_8pqCO8uam0DaedzMHghN6Ul7Q&oe=66D1B09B"}, {"file_name": "com.ypro.project_y-20240209-2137122.png", "id": "7621650634553270", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75556799_7621650644553269_1655627145384024300_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=A2cDHx5PC7kQ7kNvgF2l6pD&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCX2Gve3JTipMQY-irnXfCnA624a_TvxciQcY-7WDpzlg&oe=66D1A69D"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Project_Y: Working Title", "keywords": [], "long_description": "This game is the Japanese version.\nIt supports Japanese only.\n\n\"A true ghost story told by a person named Y.\nIt was about an investigation to find out the true meaning of a common self-inflicted urban legend that says, ``If you hear it, you'll be cursed.''\nand...\nThere is a ``sinister existence'' that appears and disappears there.\nThis project reconstructed those interview records as 360\u00b0 videos and produced and developed them as interactive content using live-action VR.\n\n\n- It comes with \"\